Today, a bit warmer for the feels like temperature (up 4.5°C) and outside temperature (up 3.4°C) and more moisture-laden outside humidity (up 9%) and rainfall (up 0.5 mm).

The past week and month had observable variation in cloud levels (up 1019 m) and light levels (up 6015 lux) when compared to today.
